criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Be older than 18 years old;

          2. Clinical or pathological diagnosis of malignant hepatobiliary tumors;

          3. Patients have received or are about to receive surgery, chemotherapy radiotherapy,
             targeted therapy, local therapy, immunotherapy, etc;

          4. Patients understand and are willing to sign written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients considered by the doctor to be unsuitable for entry into this study (mental
             disorder or poor compliance, etc.);

          2. The patient or guardian is unwilling to participate in this study;

          3. Pregnant women;

          4. Combined with other serious systemic diseases (heart failure, renal
             failure,hematopoietic system disease or Uncontrollable acute infection);

          5. Estimated survival time is less than 1 month.
